						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up Yeḍatāru-seṭṭi's hāḍi (jungle)</p>						

						<p>Circa 16th century.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record seems to register gifts of lands by several <hi rend="italic">seṭṭis.</hi> The details are all lost. On the other side of the slab is engraved. No. G. N. 437 above.</p>						

						</summary>
